data.description: Unlock the potential of this remarkable .159-acre lot nestled in the heart of coveted 78704. Here's your chance to reimagine the possibilities: renovate the original 1930s home that graces the property, or start from scratch and craft your dream residence in this highly sought-after location. Mature trees line the back side of the property providing a natural canopy that compliments the charming existing home. This cozy dwelling offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, basking in abundant natural light throughout. With city sewer and water connections in place, this lot is primed for transformation. Located just blocks away from an array of Austin's hottest restaurants and attractions, and boasting easy access to I-35, Riverside, and Lady Bird Lake, you'll relish the convenience of city living. Downtown Austin is just minutes away, offering the vibrant energy and cultural experiences that make this city renowned. This unique opportunity is tucked away in a quiet pocket, offering a lifestyle that blends urban accessibility with the tranquility of a secluded oasis. Don't let this extraordinary opportunity pass you by—take the reins and make your mark in the heart of Austin's most coveted neighborhood.
